name: Brightmoss Ape
text:
{1}, {t}, Sacrifice Brightmoss Ape: Search your library for a basic land card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
{1}, {t}, Sacrifice Brightmoss Ape: Earthshake 1. (Distribute a +1/+1 counter among up to 1 target land you control. You may have it become a 0/0 Elemental creature until end of turn. It's still a land.)
